{"title":"赠中华人民共和国文化代表团","authors":["吴努"],"dates":[{"year":1957,"month":4,"day":7}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"赠中华人民共和国文化代表团"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"缅甸联邦总理　吴努"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看她舞影蹁跹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敢夸色艺无双，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"娇娆好比天仙，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"装点更显风光。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是箫？还是胡琴？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和谐堪称绝妙，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"笙鼓声声相应——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和平、悦耳的曲调，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天上音乐的神貌！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"惊心动魄是情节，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"出神入化是刀棍，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"舞台是花花世界，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看筋斗翻转乾坤——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"合拍圆转的法轮！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"亲爱、愉快的友伴，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你们用高超的技艺，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"撒个“美达”（注）香弥漫，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"增厚了两国的情谊——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我深信；我心怀感激。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"亲爱、愉快的友伴，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你们用崇高的善意"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让人类感受到美善，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"使人人热爱真理——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我深信；我满心欢喜。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"1957年3月22日"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"译者注：“美达”是原文的译音，意谓友情。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（卞之琳译）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":7,"page_end":7}